data.description: Smyrna Townhome offers quick access to I-85, Atlanta Hwy, Atlanta and Mid Town. This 4 bedroom features rich hardwoods on the main level and an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining. You will enjoy the separate dining room, spacious great room with fireplace, gorgeous kitchen with granite counter tops, island, top of the line cabinetry, breakfast area and view to the great room! Upstairs you will find the relaxing owner's suite with spa style bath and whirlpool tub plus 2 more bedrooms & bath. The finished lower level offers an additional bedroom and bath.
